[Citation. Gannon WD , Stokes JW , Francois SA, et al. Association Between Availability of ECMO and Mortality in COVID-19 Patients Eligible for ECMO: A Natural Experiment . American Journal of Respiratory and Critical Care Medicine. https://doi.org/10.1164/rccm.202110-2399LE accepted: 24 Feb 2022]

